trans-unit.source: This plugin provides the possibility to list and show various kinds of entities of Service BW API onto your website.
Organisationseinheiten List Plugin: Effectively organizes and lists organizational units, ensuring straightforward access to relevant information.
Organisationseinheiten Show Plugin: Presents organizational units with a user-friendly interface for seamless exploration.
Services List Plugin: Efficiently organizes and lists available services, ensuring straightforward access to relevant information.
Services Show Plugin: Displays detailed information about services with a user-friendly interface for easy exploration.
Lebenslagen List Plugin: Efficiently organizes and lists essential life scenarios, ensuring straightforward access to relevant information.
Lebenslagen Show Plugin: Displays crucial life situations with a user-friendly interface for easy exploration.
Specialized in swiftly retrieving information from the BW2 service entities, ensuring precise and targeted results for an enhanced user experience.
